<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Perfil de Usuario</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ADD8E6;
            height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 5%;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .header-title {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .profile-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .profile-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .profile-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .profile-form {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .profile-picture {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            max-width: 400px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-row .form-group {
            flex: 1;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #555;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #F47272;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #F25E5E;
        }

        .profile-image {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 3px solid #F25E5E;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .edit-btn {
            background-color: #C4DB97;
            color: #333;
            border: 2px solid #98A879;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .edit-btn:hover {
            background-color: #b5d07d;
        }

        .edit-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #add8e671;
            padding: 40px 5%;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .footer-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .footer-section {
            width: 23%;
            min-width: 200px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .footer-section p, .footer-section a {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: block;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .social-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .form-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0;
            }
            
            .footer-section {
                width: 48%;
            }
            
            .profile-image {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .footer-section {
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            header {
                flex-direction: column;
                height: auto;
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .header-title {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-title">SandiMarket</div>
        <div class="user-icon">
            <img src="./img/icono.png" alt="Icono de usuario" width="40">
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="profile-container">
        <h1 class="profile-title">Tu perfil</h1>
        
        <div class="profile-content">
            <div class="profile-form">
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="nombre">Nombre</label>
                        <input type="text" id="nombre" placeholder="Tu nombre">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="apellido-paterno">Apellido Paterno</label>
                        <input type="text" id="apellido-paterno" placeholder="Apellido paterno">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="apellido-materno">Apellido Materno</label>
                    <input type="text" id="apellido-materno" placeholder="Apellido materno">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="username">Nombre de usuario</label>
                        <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Nombre de usuario">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="telefono">Número de teléfono</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="telefono" placeholder="Número de teléfono">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Correo electrónico</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Correo electrónico">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Contraseña</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Contraseña">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="profile-picture">
                <img src="/deadpool.jpeg" alt="Foto de perfil" class="profile-image">
                <button class="edit-btn">
                    <img src="./img/lapiz.png" alt="Editar" class="edit-icon">
                    Editar perfil
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>SandiMarket</h3>
                <p>Contamos con los mejores productos escolares para tu estancia en el nivel medio superior</p>
                <div class="social-icons">
                    <img src="./img/twitter.png" alt="Twitter" class="social-icon">
                    <img src="./img/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" class="social-icon">
                    <img src="./img/insta.png" alt="Instagram" class="social-icon">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>COMPAÑÍA</h3>
                <a href="#">Conócenos</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>AYUDA</h3>
                <a href="#">Detalles de entrega</a>
                <a href="#">Términos y condiciones</a>
                <a href="#">Política de privacidad</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>FAQ</h3>
                <a href="#">Cuenta</a>
                <a href="#">Entregas</a>
                <a href="#">Forma de pago</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>